item.title: By: Tisha F.
item.dc:creator: Tisha F.
item.description: I actually have that ELF blush brush. It works great although the brush came apart. But I still use it. I must admit, I left it in the car in my makeup bag in 100+ degree heat more than once so it's probably my fault. I'm sure that the glue they use is not meant to withstand that kind of abuse. That's my 2 cents.
